Package: rGetEDGAR
Title: Efficient Parallel Downloading and Processing of SEC EDGAR Filings
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Matthias", "Uckert", , "Matthias.Uckert@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for downloading and processing SEC EDGAR filings with a focus 
    on performance and reliability. Features include parallel downloading of master indices 
    and document links, rate-limited requests respecting SEC guidelines, robust error handling, 
    and efficient storage in both SQLite and Parquet formats. The package supports incremental 
    updates, automated backups, and offers a flexible filtering system for targeting specific 
    companies, document types, and time periods.
